---
import BaseLayout from "../components/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="关于 / About - MrFung" description="MrFung 的中英双语个人介绍。">
  <header class="page-intro">
    <div class="section">
      <p class="page-kicker">About</p>
      <h1>关于 / About</h1>
      <div class="bilingual intro-copy">
        <p>全栈开发者，AICoding 实践者，独立产品构建者，也是在山野和水面上练习长期主义的人。</p>
        <p>Full-stack developer, AICoding practitioner, independent product builder, and someone who practices long-term thinking on trails and water.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>
  <main>
    <section class="section">
      <div class="about-layout">
        <article class="prose-card about-main">
          <p class="meta-line">Profile</p>
          <h2>把技术、产品和行动力放在同一个节奏里。</h2>
          <div class="bilingual">
            <p>我喜欢从真实工作流出发，用全栈能力和 AICoding 把想法快速做成可用产品。相比做一次性的展示，我更在意工具能不能长期维护、持续迭代、真正帮用户少一点混乱。</p>
            <p>I like starting from real workflows, then using full-stack development and AICoding to turn ideas into usable products quickly. I care less about one-off demos and more about tools that can be maintained, improved, and genuinely reduce friction for users.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
        <aside class="profile-aside">
          <div class="bio-item">
            <strong>全栈 / Full-stack</strong>
            <span>从产品页面、工具体验到发布资料，把想法推进到真实可用。</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bio-item">
            <strong>AICoding</strong>
            <span>把 AI 辅助开发当成长期工作流的一部分，追求速度，也保留工程判断。</span>
          </div>
          <div class="bio-item">
            <strong>运动 / Outdoor</strong>
            <span>越野跑、马拉松和划桨板，让节奏、耐心和风险意识变得更具体。</span>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="section-heading">
        <h2>身份与兴趣 / Identity & Interests</h2>
        <p>把工程、产品和耐力运动放在同一个长期节奏里。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="metric-grid about-metrics">
        <div class="metric"><strong>Full-stack</strong><span>全栈开发 / Product engineering</span></div>
        <div class="metric"><strong>AICoding</strong><span>AI 辅助开发 / AI-assisted building</span></div>
        <div class="metric"><strong>ITRA 430</strong><span>越野跑积分 / Trail running index</span></div>
        <div class="metric"><strong>马拉松大众二级</strong><span>Marathon Amateur Level 2</span></div>
        <div class="metric"><strong>有为青年</strong><span>Purpose-driven young builder</span></div>
        <div class="metric"><strong>红十字救护员</strong><span>Red Cross first aider</span></div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <div class="bilingual">
        <article class="lang-card">
          <span class="lang-label">中文</span>
          <h3>山野、水面和产品</h3>
          <p>越野跑、马拉松和划桨板让我更相信稳定训练、清晰节奏和风险意识。写代码、做产品也一样：先找到真实路线，再一步一步推进。</p>
        </article>
        <article class="lang-card">
          <span class="lang-label">English</span>
          <h3>Trails, water, and product craft</h3>
          <p>Trail running, marathons, and paddleboarding reinforce the same habits I value in product work: steady practice, clear pacing, and respect for risk.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
